club.name: Hillz
club.description:
Results from each Hillz Ride, available here on wednesday evenings: 

edinburgh-hillz [dot] vercel [dot] app/results/latest

*Still being tested, results may be delayed, wrong or not appear at all!*

To be included in results, you must join this strava group and have a public ride.

See segments for each ride here: 

docs [dot] google [dot] com/document/d/1jhVRb3ry0tei7UuQBkGGG8oosxwIHXPg7pZMo8w-g30/

Historical Results available at edinburgh-hillz [dot] vercel [dot] app/results/DDMonYY
(e.g., 14Jan25)
